translateReachableExceptionHandlers

private void translateReachableExceptionHandlers()
Translates a special BoogiePL block for all the exception handlers which are reachable from the current instruction. The block assumes all the type information which is guaranteed whenever the corresponding exception handler is reached at runtime.
